Vcs-Git: git://git.debian.org/pkg-php/dh-php5.git
Vcs-Browser: http://git.debian.org/?p=pkg-php-maint/dh-php5.git;a=summary

Package: dh-php5
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, perl, debhelper
Replaces: php5-dev (<< 5.5.9+dfsg-2~)
Conflicts: php5-dev (<< 5.5.9+dfsg-2~)
Description: debhelper add-on to handle PHP PECL extensions
 dh-php5 provides a debhelper sequence add-on named 'php5' and the
 dh_php5 command.
 .
 The dh_php5 command adds the appropriate code to the postinst, prerm
 and postrm maint scripts to properly enable/disable PHP PECL
 extensions for all available PHP SAPIs.
